Key Match Events: Kyle Higashioka's solo homer started a five-run rally against an ailing Max Fried with two outs in the second inning
Harris II homered to center (414 feet), Arcia scored in the 8th inning
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the second game of the NL Wild Card Series between the San Diego Padres and Atlanta Braves
Others: The game was played at Petco Park in San Diego, California, and was attended by 47,705 fans
